flowchart LR
    DEV[Developer commit] --> GH[GitHub main branch]
    GH --> GHA[GitHub Actions workflow]
    GHA --> LINT[Lint + type check]
    LINT --> TEST[Pytest suite]
    TEST --> BUILD[Docker build + tag]
    BUILD --> REG[Container registry]
    REG --> K8S[kubectl apply manifests]
    K8S --> ROLL[Rolling update Pods]
